parameters.text:
=You are a recruitment AI assistant. Analyze if this candidate matches the job requirements.

Candidate Profile:
{{ $json.text }}

Job Requirements:
- Position: {{ $('Airtable - Get Job Requirements').item.json.Position }}
- Required Experience: {{ $('Airtable - Get Job Requirements').item.json.Required_Experience }} years
- Required Skills: {{ $('Airtable - Get Job Requirements').item.json.Required_Skills }}
- Education Required: {{ $('Airtable - Get Job Requirements').item.json.Education_Required }}
- Nice to Have: {{ $('Airtable - Get Job Requirements').item.json.Nice_To_Have }}

Provide:
1. Match Score (0-100)
2. Qualification Status (Highly Qualified / Qualified / Potentially Qualified / Not Qualified)
3. Strengths (3 key points)
4. Gaps (areas where candidate doesn't meet requirements)
5. Recommendation (Interview / Phone Screen / Reject)

Format as JSON: {"match_score": number, "status": string, "strengths": [string], "gaps": [string], "recommendation": string, "reasoning": string}

=Generate a personalized recruitment email for this candidate.

Candidate: {{ $('Airtable - Store Candidate').item.json.Name }}
Position: {{ $('Webhook - Receive CV').item.json.body.position }}
Match Score: {{ $json.match_score }}
Status: {{ $json.status }}
Recommendation: {{ $json.recommendation }}

Key Strengths:
{{ $json.strengths.join('\n') }}

Email should:
- Be professional and warm
- Congratulate them on their application
- Mention 1-2 specific strengths that stood out
- {{ $json.recommendation === 'Interview' ? 'Invite them for a formal interview' : 'Suggest a preliminary phone screening' }}
- Include next steps
- Be concise (150-200 words)

Provide: {"subject": string, "body": string}

=üéØ *New Candidate Processed*

*Candidate:* {{ $('Airtable - Store Candidate').item.json.Name }}
*Position:* {{ $('Webhook - Receive CV').item.json.body.position }}
*Match Score:* {{ $('AI Agent - Qualification Assessment').item.json.match_score }}%
*Status:* {{ $('AI Agent - Qualification Assessment').item.json.status }}
*Recommendation:* {{ $('AI Agent - Qualification Assessment').item.json.recommendation }}

*Key Strengths:*
{{ $('AI Agent - Qualification Assessment').item.json.strengths.map((s, i) => `${i+1}. ${s}`).join('\n') }}

{{ $('AI Agent - Qualification Assessment').item.json.recommendation === 'Interview' ? 'üìÖ *Interview Scheduled:* ' + $now.plus({ days: 3 }).toFormat('MMM dd, yyyy HH:mm') : 'üìû *Next Step:* Phone screening' }}

<https://airtable.com/appXXXXXXXXXXXXXX/tblCandidates/{{ $('Airtable - Store Candidate').item.json.id }}|View in Airtable>

